title: 725. Week 5 Big Games, Rookie Report Card, Closers & Rookie Pass Catchers
itunes:title: 725. Week 5 Big Games, Rookie Report Card, Closers & Rookie Pass Catchers
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis look back at the weekend and all the action from Week 5 of the NFL season. The guys start by breaking down the big 3 games from Sunday. Next, the trio look at which teams lost certain aspects and which teams found parts of their play this week. After that, the guys discuss 8 Week 5 closers. Then, the trio give a grade to the rookies that played based off their Week 5 performances. To wrap up the show, DJ, Bucky and Rhett break down rookie pass catchers that are catching on.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
